# Line endings: LF in the repository and in every working tree.
# Windows is the sole runtime target, but the toolchain enforces LF
# (Prettier `endOfLine: lf`, ESLint), so a CRLF checkout fails the lint
# gate on every file. Pin LF here so `core.autocrlf` can't reintroduce CRLF.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Known binary assets — never normalize (protects current/future fixtures,
# voice models, and native addons from line-ending corruption).
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.wav   binary
*.mp3   binary
*.onnx  binary
*.bin   binary
*.node  binary
*.dll   binary
*.exe   binary
*.zip   binary
